Interface Decorator<T>

Type Parameters:
T - service type
All Superinterfaces:
Ordered
All Known Implementing Classes:
DecoratorImpl
public interface Decorator<T>
extends Ordered

This class represents service decorator definition that distributively decorates services. By default it is configured by module decorate methods annotated with Decorate class.

Since:
1.0
Author:
